1
00:00:29,430 --> 00:00:31,430
I thought they didn't have the guts.

2
00:00:32,460 --> 00:00:33,300
It seems

3
00:00:33,830 --> 00:00:36,700
I still underestimated the madness of these hypocrites.

4
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:38,400
Master, what happened?

5
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:39,660
It's fine.

6
00:00:40,630 --> 00:00:42,360
You stay here and protect them.

7
00:00:42,530 --> 00:00:43,300
I

8
00:00:43,860 --> 00:00:44,920
will be right back.

9
00:00:54,460 --> 00:00:55,990
Ultimate Imperial Weapon.

10
00:00:56,460 --> 00:00:58,460
Is the Human Ancestral Court crazy?

11
00:01:04,260 --> 00:01:05,360
The Land of the Sin Clan

12
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:06,460
cannot be lost.

13
00:01:06,900 --> 00:01:09,030
Even if we start an imperial war today,

14
00:01:09,260 --> 00:01:11,960
we must keep Gu Linyuan here forever.

15
00:01:12,300 --> 00:01:15,630
Do you really think our Human Ancestral Court is like Taixuan Sacred Land,

16
00:01:15,630 --> 00:01:16,860
a soft target,

17
00:01:17,130 --> 00:01:19,630
that Gu Linyuan can easily manipulate?

18
00:01:38,100 --> 00:01:40,500
Slaughtering innocent mortals at will...

19
00:01:41,729 --> 00:01:42,530
You guys

20
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:46,160
really deserve the name of the Human Ancestral Court.

21
00:01:46,160 --> 00:01:46,960
Old Demon Gu,

22
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,960
instead of staying quietly in the Eastern Wasteland,

23
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,900
you came to the Central Continent to meddle in our affairs.

24
00:01:50,900 --> 00:01:52,229
Today I will let you know

25
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:53,600
that there are some things in this world

26
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:55,460
you can't meddle with just because you want to.

27
00:01:55,460 --> 00:01:56,130
Oh?

28
00:01:56,830 --> 00:01:59,160
Just sending four peak Great Sages

29
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,430
to kill me?

30
00:02:01,100 --> 00:02:02,000
Are you

31
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:05,300
looking down on me too much?

32
00:02:05,660 --> 00:02:06,560
To kill you,

33
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:08,729
the four of us with the Imperial Weapon

34
00:02:08,729 --> 00:02:09,960
are more than enough.

35
00:02:10,630 --> 00:02:11,660
Kunwu Seal!

36
00:02:11,860 --> 00:02:13,960
Suppress him!

37
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:22,690
Carrying a broken seal forged by someone else

38
00:02:22,730 --> 00:02:24,500
is your trump card?

39
00:02:37,329 --> 00:02:38,600
Your realm...

40
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:39,660
You...

41
00:02:40,100 --> 00:02:41,630
You are about to achieve the Dao.

42
00:02:41,630 --> 00:02:44,100
You are not at the early stage of Prospective Emperor at all.

43
00:02:44,100 --> 00:02:44,530
You

44
00:02:44,860 --> 00:02:47,130
are already on the verge of the Great Emperor Realm.

45
00:02:47,130 --> 00:02:49,300
It seems your Ancestral Court's intelligence network

46
00:02:49,300 --> 00:02:50,560
is a bit outdated.

47
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:52,130
I

48
00:02:52,660 --> 00:02:55,060
have long been invincible in this world.

49
00:03:05,630 --> 00:03:10,200
Revive, Kunwu Seal!

50
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:30,230
Since you delivered yourself all the way here,

51
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:31,930
if I let you escape,

52
00:03:32,460 --> 00:03:34,500
wouldn't it be impolite of me?

53
00:03:39,860 --> 00:03:40,460
Suppress!

54
00:03:47,630 --> 00:03:49,690
This is an Ultimate Imperial Weapon!

55
00:03:50,030 --> 00:03:52,360
A weapon that can easily destroy a domain!

56
00:03:52,460 --> 00:03:54,500
What realm is Master in now?

57
00:03:54,900 --> 00:03:57,530
He can suppress an awakened Imperial Weapon effortlessly.

58
00:03:57,530 --> 00:03:59,100
Master.

59
00:03:59,700 --> 00:04:01,330
You killed the ancestors of the four families

60
00:04:01,330 --> 00:04:03,000
and took the Xiao family's Imperial Weapon.

61
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:03,660
Next,

62
00:04:03,730 --> 00:04:05,400
are we in big trouble?

63
00:04:05,630 --> 00:04:06,230
No,

64
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,600
Qingchen.

65
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:08,900
You are wrong.

66
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:12,660
They are the ones in big trouble.

67
00:04:12,900 --> 00:04:17,029
The Human Ancestral Court tried hard to hide the dirty secrets of the Sin Village.

68
00:04:17,029 --> 00:04:19,829
But now, not only did the four ancestors die tragically,

69
00:04:19,829 --> 00:04:22,830
even the Xiao family's foundational Imperial Weapon is lost.

70
00:04:22,830 --> 00:04:24,660
Who do you think is more anxious?

71
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:29,830
Patriarch!

72
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:32,560
The ancestor died tragically and his life tablet shattered.

73
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:35,659
Even our Xiao family's supreme Imperial Weapon, the Kunwu Seal,

74
00:04:35,659 --> 00:04:38,159
has completely lost its connection!

75
00:04:38,500 --> 00:04:39,630
Gu Linyuan!

76
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:42,030
How dare he?

77
00:04:42,159 --> 00:04:43,630
Ring the assembly bell.

78
00:04:43,730 --> 00:04:46,200
Recall all clansmen outside immediately

79
00:04:46,530 --> 00:04:48,530
to follow me to the human ancestral court

80
00:04:48,530 --> 00:04:50,330
and ask Her Majesty for justice.

81
00:04:50,330 --> 00:04:51,100
This old demon Gu

82
00:04:51,100 --> 00:04:52,000
is acting so recklessly.

83
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:56,400
Does he really want to make an enemy of the entire human race?
